"border: 1px solid #875A7B; border-radius: 3px\">\n"
"            ເບິ່ງ</a>\n"
"    </div>\n"
"    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr>\n"
"        <td width=\"130px;\" style=\"min-width: 130px;\">\n"
